This list can be filtered by common crop name to narrow results to a specific crop. parameters: - name: abbreviation description: Filter by program abbreviation. Exact match. in: query required: false schema: type: string - name: programType description: |- The type of program entity this object represents
'STANARD' represents a standard, permenant breeding program
